        "subject": "LU-4665 osd: to make zfs work on PPC nodes",
        "message": "LU-4665 osd: to make zfs work on PPC nodes\n\nTwo fixes:\n1.in llog_osd_{next,prev}_block(), tail has already swapped so not\n  necessary to swap it again;\n2. it's incorrect to load zfs library with a specific version. Zfs\n  on linux has updated its version number to 2.\n\nSigned-off-by: Jinshan Xiong <jinshan.xiong@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ifc2609d37f3d75761e25ba4ab44fb8af05054641\n"
